---
<section class="testimonials" id="testimonials">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-eyebrow reveal">Community voices</div>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal reveal-d1">Stories from<br>our community</h2>
    <p class="section-desc reveal reveal-d2">Real words from the people who make Bloom what it is.</p>
    <div class="testimonials-grid">
      <div class="testimonial-card reveal reveal-d1">
        <div class="stars">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 1l2.2 4.4L15 6.1l-3.5 3.4.8 4.8L8 12.2 3.7 14.3l.8-4.8L1 6.1l4.8-.7z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 1l2.2 4.4L15 6.1l-3.5 3.4.8 4.8L8 12.2 3.7 14.3l.8-4.8L1 6.1l4.8-.7z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 1l2.2 4.4L15 6.1l-3.5 3.4.8 4.8L8 12.2 3.7 14.3l.8-4.8L1 6.1l4.8-.7z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 1l2.2 4.4L15 6.1l-3.5 3.4.8 4.8L8 12.2 3.7 14.3l.8-4.8L1 6.1l4.8-.7z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 1l2.2 4.4L15 6.1l-3.5 3.4.8 4.8L8 12.2 3.7 14.3l.8-4.8L1 6.1l4.8-.7z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <blockquote>I never knew flowers could feel this personal. The seasonal curation changed how I decorate my entire home.</blockquote>
        <div class="author">
          <img class="author-avatar" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?w=80&h=80&fit=crop&crop=face&fm=webp" alt="Elena M." width="40" height="40" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
          <div>
            <div class="author-name">Elena M.</div>
            <div class="author-role">Interior stylist, Portland</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-card reveal reveal-d2">
        <div class="stars">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 1l2.2 4.4L15 6.1l-3.5 3.4.8 4.8L8 12.2 3.7 14.3l.8-4.8L1 6.1l4.8-.7z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 1l2.2 4.4L15 6.1l-3.5 3.4.8 4.8L8 12.2 3.7 14.3l.8-4.8L1 6.1l4.8-.7z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 1l2.2 4.4L15 6.1l-3.5 3.4.8 4.8L8 12.2 3.7 14.3l.8-4.8L1 6.1l4.8-.7z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 1l2.2 4.4L15 6.1l-3.5 3.4.8 4.8L8 12.2 3.7 14.3l.8-4.8L1 6.1l4.8-.7z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 1l2.2 4.4L15 6.1l-3.5 3.4.8 4.8L8 12.2 3.7 14.3l.8-4.8L1 6.1l4.8-.7z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <blockquote>The care guides are a lifesaver. My kitchen counter used to be a flower graveyard. Now everything lasts two weeks.</blockquote>
        <div class="author">
          <img class="author-avatar" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=80&h=80&fit=crop&crop=face&fm=webp" alt="James K." width="40" height="40" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
          <div>
            <div class="author-name">James K.</div>
            <div class="author-role">Home cook, Brooklyn</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-card reveal reveal-d3">
        <div class="stars">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 1l2.2 4.4L15 6.1l-3.5 3.4.8 4.8L8 12.2 3.7 14.3l.8-4.8L1 6.1l4.8-.7z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 1l2.2 4.4L15 6.1l-3.5 3.4.8 4.8L8 12.2 3.7 14.3l.8-4.8L1 6.1l4.8-.7z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 1l2.2 4.4L15 6.1l-3.5 3.4.8 4.8L8 12.2 3.7 14.3l.8-4.8L1 6.1l4.8-.7z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 1l2.2 4.4L15 6.1l-3.5 3.4.8 4.8L8 12.2 3.7 14.3l.8-4.8L1 6.1l4.8-.7z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 1l2.2 4.4L15 6.1l-3.5 3.4.8 4.8L8 12.2 3.7 14.3l.8-4.8L1 6.1l4.8-.7z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <blockquote>I gifted the wildflower bundle to my mom and she cried happy tears. That is the power of good flowers.</blockquote>
        <div class="author">
          <img class="author-avatar" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1438761681033-6461ffad8d80?w=80&h=80&fit=crop&crop=face&fm=webp" alt="Priya S." width="40" height="40" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
          <div>
            <div class="author-name">Priya S.</div>
            <div class="author-role">Architect, Austin</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
